thread.title: BRIEF-Nasdaq January 2018 Volumes

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Nasdaq January 2018 Volumes
text:
Feb 5 (Reuters) - Nasdaq Inc:
* NASDAQ JANUARY 2018 VOLUMES * NASDAQ INC - JANUARY U.S. EQUITY OPTIONS VOLUME 165 MILLION CONTRACTS VERSUS 129 MILLION CONTRACTS LAST YEAR
* NASDAQ INC - JANUARY EUROPEAN OPTIONS AND FUTURES VOLUME 6.7 MILLION CONTRACTS VERSUS 6.9 MILLION CONTRACTS
* NASDAQ INC - JANUARY U.S. FIXED INCOME VOLUME $1,627 BILLION TRADED VERSUS $1,686 BILLION TRADED Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
